note right
{
  "AccountNumber": CIF + GoalCode + ReferenceNo,
  "Name": Portfolio Name,
  "BranchId": {branchId},
  "CurrencyId": currencyId, // 34 for IDR
  "ContactGroupId": {contactGroupId},
  "AccountType": 2,
  "Balance": 0,
  "IsActive": true,
  "Product": {productId},
  "Status": 1
}
end note
activate dfs
dfs --> ms: return accountId
